the people who are not in mega-guilds.  Or maybe they are just listening to<br />
the buzz from CoH and trying to pick up on something that seems to be<br />
working I don't know.<br />
<br />
But over all... the #1 thing they list is fixing something with the<br />
freaking Plane of Time???  Um... I don't think they really get it.<br />
